{"tid":2391851,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅顴骨激凸兼右眼合唔埋 網民：撞樣木偶Billy","createTime":"2021-02-02T12:40:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T14:35:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d89bbddbbc45453a2037040bd5921f6c68a58aee","tid":2391851,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0kboHMfEREy6xRAnxeVLtI5Viw0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5PKPIKJ7CNEZHHTNAMEEXXEPRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0kboHMfEREy6xRAnxeVLtI5Viw0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5PKPIKJ7CNEZHHTNAMEEXXEPRY.jpg&h=7e33813f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現年28歲的韓國「馬舞女」泫雅，出道以來樣貌變化都很大，前年陷整容疑雲，嘴唇變得豐厚遭質疑做了豐唇手術，事後泫雅在IG發文否認有豐唇，解釋因愛化over lip的妝容才形成這樣的效果。不過近日泫雅到各大電視台力谷新歌《I&rsquo;m Not Cool》時，又被網民指臉整壞了，右眼更似合不起來，當中臉頰的顴骨離奇凸出，似足木偶Billy，網民質疑她再度整容外，亦指她似老了10年。<br />\n<br />\n網民擔心健康狀況<br />\n未知是否因為化妝效果關係，泫雅連日來在台上演繹《I&rsquo;m Not Cool》時，可見其右眼似合不埋，有網民更揚言近日看她的表演時就會覺得她變成「獨眼龍」，亦有網民覺得她右眼似乎不適或者受了傷，才會出現這個情況。有網民就擔心泫雅之前患上因血管迷走神經性昏厥復發，令她的健康亮紅燈，亦擔心泫雅仍未完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zN1MwtcmuuIHgt1sEk_SuiINgM4=/802x1373/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JUBRZRBV7FCUJGOSZOE3ECTH24.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzN1MwtcmuuIHgt1sEk_SuiINgM4%3D%2F802x1373%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJUBRZRBV7FCUJGOSZOE3ECTH24.JPG&h=9ec86046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PNe477oKgtAn_6hOgWbEen-Z_6k=/802x1337/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BQA3PT5PT5DVXKAEFPDALE3RDE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPNe477oKgtAn_6hOgWbEen-Z_6k%3D%2F802x1337%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBQA3PT5PT5DVXKAEFPDALE3RDE.JPG&h=9f674735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_qj9fNzHNmtZjyYdW16TF3682ys=/802x418/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7MWYUMV5ZNDL7I64G62EU3HXDQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_qj9fNzHNmtZjyYdW16TF3682ys%3D%2F802x418%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7MWYUMV5ZNDL7I64G62EU3HXDQ.JPG&h=e3581e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zc6k1AcsdgwThwDWWAXXHEODKOs=/802x1249/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A62XBHYAGRABJDL6SCYVEDAZRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZc6k1AcsdgwThwDWWAXXHEODKOs%3D%2F802x1249%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA62XBHYAGRABJDL6SCYVEDAZRU.jpg&h=e53db638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d9a90b099772e184a67c08f14477c457097b6ce","tid":2391851,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"白粉婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c626db376e6c5f25ec63d58e2dcbd3cf3e717ba","tid":2391851,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d9a90b099772e184a67c08f14477c457097b6ce","tid":2391851,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"白粉婆<img src=\"/assets/faces